cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a novel data structure for 3D shape analysis using convolutional neural networks (CNNs). This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the efficiency of the CNN operations, which suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
